# info
http://www.discogs.com/release/3592375
Джазовый ансамбль Игоря Бриля
LP “Перед заходом солнца” aka “Twilight”
Recorded 1980-84, released 1985
Мелодия LP С60 21873 003

1985 is kinda late for my taste but this LP is still enjoyable. And there is a totally beautiful fragment in the most end of the second track - it's below. 

The more I listen to this album the more I like it - that's a reflection of its jazz nature.

[igor brill - twilight 1985 fragment.mp3] 

# tracks
